msgid "<i>Your house has burned to the ground.</i>"
msgstr "<i>你的房子被烧毁。</i>"

msgid "your house has burned to the ground."
msgstr "你的房子被烧毁。"

msgid "The woman came to you in a panic, raving about monsters emerging from the ground in a home near Rivertown. “I managed to trap them,” she explains, “but there are others. Other pits. Other domains.” Only last week, you would have thought she was a lunatic. Recent events, however, have challenged your preconceptions of normality. You decide to hear her out. She introduces herself as Lita Chantler and lays out a tale that strains the limits of your belief. “The creatures I speak of ,” she claims, “are called ghouls—cruel beings who plague the crypts, caverns, and tunnels beneath the city of Arkham…”"
msgstr ""
"一名神色惊慌的女子向你们走来，呓语着怪物从河岸城附近一间民宅的地下钻了出来。“我设法困住了它们，”她解释道，“但是还有其他怪物。其他地穴。其他巢穴。”如若在上周，你一定会认为她发疯了。然而最近发生的诡异事件，委实动摇了你对于何谓正常的先入之见。你决定听她说完。\n"
"她自称丽塔·钱德勒并讲述了一个令人难以置信的故事。“我所说的怪物，”她声称，“叫做食尸鬼——一种滋生在阿卡姆城地穴、岩洞和隧道里的残忍生物……”"

msgid "In the wake of the disaster at your home, Lita Chantler, the red-haired woman from your parlor, lays out a tale that—even in light of what you have just witnessed—strains the limits of your belief. “The creatures in your home,” she claims, “are called ghouls—cruel beings who plague the crypts, caverns, and tunnels beneath the city of Arkham…”"
msgstr "丽塔·钱德勒，这个出现在你客厅中的红发女子，在你家遇灾之后将真相和盘托出——即便你已在自己家中瞥见了其中的一些光景——她所说之事还是挑战着你所信的极限。“你宅邸里的怪物，”她声称，“叫做食尸鬼——一种滋生在阿卡姆城地穴、岩洞和隧道里的残忍生物……””"

msgid ""
"“These creatures feed on the corpses of humans, and they are served by a dark cult within Arkham whose members have inexplicably come to worship the ancient master of the ghouls. This cult has been killing innocent people and feeding them to the ghouls, satiating a monstrous hunger. A dark balance was maintained. Until now. Recently,” Lita continues, “one of their lairs, where the corpses were stored, was destroyed. Since then, the ghouls have been more active than usual. I have tracked their movements and tried my best to stop them from running amok throughout the city. But I think there is something worse going on. The cult has been planning something darker, and more ominous, than anything I have yet observed. Indications are that this plan shall come to fruition tonight, shortly after midnight. Beyond that, I cannot fathom what to expect.\n"
"“Many of the cultists,” Lita continues, “will seem like everyday people, despite their foul intentions. Whenever the cult meets, its members don masks shaped like the skulls of various animals to protect their identities from one another. These masks are our mark. Symbols of death and decay. We must unmask the cultists to expose and derail their plans. We have but a few hours. The more cultists we find before midnight, the better.”"
msgstr ""
"“这些怪物以人类的尸体为食，而阿卡姆城内存在着侍奉它们的黑暗异教，教徒秘密地崇拜着食尸鬼的远古主人。教徒会不时杀戮无辜，以投喂食尸鬼，满足它们骇人听闻的饥饿。而一种黑暗的平衡就这样维持着。现在一切都变了。最近，”丽塔接着说道，“一个食尸鬼储藏尸体的巢穴被摧毁了。自那时起，食尸鬼的活动变得异常频繁。我追踪它们的活动轨迹并竭尽全力阻止它们，不让它们在城中胡作非为。然而，我担心更加糟糕的情况正在发生。异教正在谋划某种更为黑暗、更为不详的东西，远超我之前所见。种种迹象表明该计划将在今晚午夜后不久得以实现。除此之外，我无法揣测将会发生什么。”\n"
"“许多异教徒，”丽塔接着说道，“虽然心怀恶意，看上去却与常人无异。他们集会时将头戴各种动物头骨造型的假面，以防彼此间暴露身份。这些假面正是我们要寻找的记号。那是死亡与腐败的符号。我们必须找出那些异教徒，揭露并阻挠他们的计划。留给我们的时间只剩几个小时了。午夜之前，我们找出的异教徒越多越好。”"

msgid "Set the <i>Cult of Umôrdhoth</i> encounter set aside as a separate “Cultist deck,” and shuffle it."
msgstr "将<i>默尔多斯的异教徒</i>遭遇组放在一边，设置为独立的“异教徒牌库“并混洗。"

msgid "Choose one of the two Downtown locations and one of the two Southside locations at random and put them into play. Remove the other versions of Downtown and Southside from the game. Then, put the Northside, Easttown, Rivertown, St. Mary’s Hospital, Graveyard, Miskatonic University, and Your House locations into play."
msgstr "在两张商业区地点和两张南区地点中各随机选择一张放置入场。将未选中的商业区和南区地点从游戏中移除。然后，将北区、东城区、河岸城、圣玛丽医院、墓地、米斯卡塔尼克大学和你的房子地点放置入场。"

msgid "No changes are made."
msgstr "不作改动。"

msgid "Search the gathered encounter sets for 1 copy of Acolyte and spawn it at Southside."
msgstr "查找收齐的遭遇组，找出1张祭司，将其生成在南区。"

msgid "Search the gathered encounter sets for 2 copies of Acolyte. Spawn 1 at Southside and 1 at Downtown."
msgstr "查找收齐的遭遇组，找出2张祭司，将1张生成在南区，1张生成在商业区。"

msgid "Search the gathered encounter sets for 3 copies of Acolyte. Spawn 1 at Southside, 1 at Downtown, and 1 at the Graveyard."
msgstr "查找收齐的遭遇组，找出3张祭司，将1张生成在南区，另1张生成在商业区，最后1张生成在墓地。"

msgid "Remove Your House from the game. Each investigator begins play at Rivertown."
msgstr "将你的房子从游戏中移除。每位调查员从河岸城开始游戏。"

msgid "Each investigator begins play at Your House."
msgstr "每位调查员从你的房子开始游戏。"

msgid "Shuffle the Ghoul Priest into the encounter deck."
msgstr "将食尸鬼祭司混洗入遭遇牌库。"

msgid "Note: Some effects first encountered in this scenario may cause doom to be placed on enemies. Remember that doom on enemies counts toward the amount of doom that will advance the agenda."
msgstr "<b>注</b>：在本冒险中首次出现的某些效果可以在敌人卡牌上放置毁灭标记。放置在敌人卡牌上的毁灭标记计入推进密谋的毁灭总数。"

msgid "In your Campaign Log, under “Cultists We Interrogated,” record the names of each unique Cultist enemy in the victory display."
msgstr "在剧本日志中的“盘问过的异教徒“一栏中，记录下每个位于胜利区的独特[[异教徒]]敌人的姓名。"

msgid "Interrogated"
msgstr "盘问过"

msgid "In your Campaign Log, under “Cultists Who Got Away,” record the name of each unique enemy still remaining in the Cultist deck or in play. If it is Agenda 1, record “The Masked Hunter” under “Cultists Who Got Away” as well."
msgstr "在剧本日志中的“未落网的异教徒“一栏中，记录下每个仍在场上或者异教徒牌库中的独特敌人的姓名。如果当前密谋是密谋1，同时在此栏记录下“假面猎手“。"

msgid "Got away"
msgstr "未落网"

msgid "In your Campaign Log, under “Cultists Who Got Away,” record the name of each unique enemy still remaining in the Cultist deck or in play."
msgstr "在剧本日志中的“未落网的异教徒“一栏中，记录下每个仍在场上或者异教徒牌库中的独特敌人的姓名。"

msgid "Is the Ghoul Priest in the victory display?"
msgstr "食尸鬼祭司是否在胜利区？"

msgid "it is past midnight."
msgstr "午夜已过。"

msgid "You’ve managed to obtain some useful information about the cult and its plans. You can only hope it’s enough."
msgstr "你尽力获得了一些关于异教徒及其计划的有用信息。你只能希望这已经足够。"

msgid "Twelve bells ring out, signaling midnight. You’re out of time; the cult’s ritual will begin shortly. You’ve managed to obtain some useful information about the cult and its plans. You can only hope it’s enough."
msgstr "钟声敲响了十二次，午夜已至。没有时间了；异教仪式即将开始。你尽力获得了一些关于异教徒及其计划的有用信息。你只能希望这已经足够。"
